act: Newspapers, Printers, and Reading Rooms Repeal Act 1869
section_title: Acts and parts of Acts in first schedule repealed, except as in second schedule.
section_text: 1  . . . . . .   The provisions of the . . . . . .   Acts which are set out in the second schedule to this Act shall continue in force in the same manner as if they were enacted in the body of this Act; . . . . . .

act: Newspapers, Printers, and Reading Rooms Repeal Act 1869
section_text: 2 This Act may be cited as The Newspapers, Printers, and Reading Rooms Repeal Act 1869.
